06:44.654 --> 06:45.940
<i>Like a dirty scalp.</i>

06:46.823 --> 06:47.984
<i>Like her shit.</i>

06:48.992 --> 06:52.235
<i>Soft, unformed, blameless.</i>

06:54.623 --> 06:55.955
