<i>They're not real, you know.</i>

07:43.004 --> 07:44.040
<i>They're not.</i>

08:47.444 --> 08:51.734
<i>Maybe I'm crazy and this is
some new kind of therapy.</i>

08:53.408 --> 08:56.776
<i>I wish that were true,
then I could get better.</i>

08:57.579 --> 09:00.913
<i>And this would go away.
