it's not so bad.

12:18.404 --> 12:21.112
- May this child grow in the grace...
- It's gross.

12:21.199 --> 12:23.691
- ...and knowledge of Our Heavenly Father.
- It's not fair.

12:24.035 --> 12:25.888
