12:29.874 --> 12:32.491
All right, girls, let's give them room
to do their work.

12:33.878 --> 12:34.914
Come on.

12:35.672 --> 12:37.208
Excuse me, ladies.

12:37.298 --> 12:39.790
What challenges has
the Lord given us this morning?

12:40.009 --> 12:42.376
Her pressure's
creeping up again. 145 over 110.

12:42.512 --> 12:45.425
Push 200 milligrams of Labetalol
and draw for labs.

12:45.556 --> 12:46.797
White count first.

12:47.308 --> 12:49.265
Now, how's our patient?

12:53.815 --> 12:54.855
Fetal heart rate
is stable.

12:55.024 --> 12:57.311
Oh, praise be.
Let's keep it that way.

13:06.828 --> 13:07.828
What's happening?

