the seizures,

14:28.201 --> 14:29.863
and our little miracle

14:30.536 --> 14:32.994
needs plenty of fluids.

14:33.206 --> 14:34.572
Ah, of course.

14:35.041 --> 14:38.910
Tie and anchor that suture closed, please.
Don't worry about the scar.

14:39.337 --> 14:40.373
Glory be with you.

14:40.588 --> 14:41.795
Ah, go in grace.

14:46.219 --> 14:50.463
The miracles God allows
these doctors to perform.

14:51.391 --> 14:53.132
