14:56.270 --> 14:59.388
Well, under His eye, dear.

15:02.777 --> 15:03.858
Hold on a minute.

15:06.614 --> 15:07.614
Pardon?

15:09.117 --> 15:10.483
I'm sorry. Um...

15:12.870 --> 15:14.031
Aunt Lydia...

15:16.874 --> 15:18.536
May I go home, please?

15:20.878 --> 15:24.462
No. You may not.
Ridiculous!

15:26.467 --> 15:27.467
Please.

15:28.177 --> 15:31.887
You may go home
when your walking partner goes home.

15:33.349 --> 15:37.218
You certainly owe her that consideration
after the way you have treated her.

15:38.271 --> 15:41.014
I know.
I know I was shitty.

15:41.774 --> 15:42.810
Ofjoseph.

15:45.570 --> 15:47.106
All you girls,
just awful.

15:47.947 --> 15:50.234
I know. I know. I...

15:52.076 --> 15:53.283
I don't feel well.

15:59.041 --> 16:00.077
Ofjoseph,

16:01.502 --> 16:02.834
I believe in you.

16:04.547 --> 16:06.914
God never gives us more
than we can handle.

16:09.552 --> 16:10.668
Are you sure?

16:11.888 --> 16:13.880
Pray without ceasing.

16:15.266 --> 16:16.302
