another procedure.

20:04.620 --> 20:05.701
Oh.

20:08.624 --> 20:09.705
Oh.

20:16.298 --> 20:17.898
I haven't been
praying for her.

20:20.052 --> 20:21.088
Not really.

20:22.972 --> 20:24.008
Okay.

20:28.227 --> 20:29.559
She had that seizure.

20:32.857 --> 20:34.644
