your fault?

20:37.361 --> 20:38.397
Obviously.

20:45.661 --> 20:46.993
Do you think
she can hear me?

20:49.999 --> 20:51.206
I don't know.

20:56.964 --> 20:58.000
Hi, Natalie.

20:59.759 --> 21:00.840
It's Janine.

21:04.847 --> 21:07.464
I just want you to know
that I forgive you.

21:10.936 --> 21:12.302
And I want you to get better.

21:17.276 --> 21:18.608
She can't get better.

21:21.447 --> 21:22.813
I can wish for it anyway.

21:31.624 --> 21:33.035
I want you to find peace.

21:37.004 --> 21:38.245
Is that better?

21:45.679 --> 21:46.715
Janine.

21:50.810 --> 21:52.426
I know
how we can help her.

22:17.419 --> 22:18.876
- No.
- Janine,

22:19.755 --> 22:21.166
it's the right thing to do.

22:23.133 --> 22:24.169
Listen to me.

22:26.804 --> 22:27.885
We have to end it.

22:29.098 --> 22:30.218
So you're going to kill her?

22:33.727 --> 22:34.808
And the baby?

22:37.231 --> 22:38.472
What did they ever
do to you?

22:42.027 --> 22:44.610
Janine, we have to.
We have to do something.

22:46.240 --> 22:47.276
Don't do that.

22:51.996 --> 22:53.237
She's one of us.

23:09.346 --> 23:10.382
Okay.

23:12.850 --> 23:13.886
Okay?

23:16.729 --> 23:17.810
Yeah.

23:19.982 --> 23:21.848
Okay. Okay.

23:28.157 --> 23:29.273
Give that to me.

23:44.381 --> 23:46.338
When did you get to be
so selfish?

23:48.510 --> 23:52.049
Everything is always
about you now. Your problems.

23:55.517 --> 23:56.974
Get the fuck out of here.

24:02.232 --> 24:03.598
You're different.

24:08.656 --> 24:10.113
I don't like it.

24:31.095 --> 24:33.838
The lungs aren't fully formed yet,
and won't be for a few weeks,

24:33.931 --> 24:36.639
