in the NICU, if need be.

24:42.022 --> 24:43.917
They're not gonna
come in here, are they?

24:43.941 --> 24:46.103
- Those sick girls?
- They're not sick.

24:46.819 --> 24:48.481
They're here for
their menarche exam.

24:49.822 --> 24:51.939
They've flowered?
How lovely.

24:52.700 --> 24:54.316
<i>That will be Hannah soon.</i>

24:55.744 --> 24:57.030
<i>Too soon.</i>

24:57.121 --> 25:00.034
It'll be a few years before they're ready
to have babies of their own.

25:02.960 --> 25:05.577
<i>He doesn't mean
emotionally ready.</i>

25:05.671 --> 25:08.288
<i>He means they track
their pelvic development.</i>

25:11.802 --> 25:13.338
<i>She's got prominent veins.</i>

25:14.179 --> 25:15.761
<i>Easy to slice, I'd think.</i>

25:17.391 --> 25:18.802
<i>His aren't bad either.</i>

25:19.643 --> 25:21.009
<i>Harder to see.</i>

25:22.646 --> 25:25.480
<i>If I only get one kill,
I should start at the top.</i>

25:25.607 --> 25:26.848
<i>Make it count.</i>

25:30.029 --> 25:31.110
<i>Eenie,</i>

25:33.157 --> 25:34.193
<i>meenie...</i>

25:35.492 --> 25:36.608
<i>...minie,</i>

25:41.040 --> 25:42.656
<i>moe.</i>

25:42.750 --> 25:44.352
I'm sorry
I couldn't get here sooner.

25:44.376 --> 25:45.854
Oh, that's all right.
Thank you for coming.

25:45.878 --> 25:47.790
Of course.
I've been praying for you.

25:47.880 --> 25:49.121
And I for you.

25:49.548 --> 25:50.959
Our precious babies.

25:51.050 --> 25:54.384
Commander, we can discuss
the rest of the lab tests in my office.

25:59.683 --> 26:02.517
Mrs. Waterford, may I speak
to you for a moment?

26:06.732 --> 26:08.394
You don't want
to bother with that.

26:12.112 --> 26:13.648
I'll catch up
with you downstairs.

26:21.914 --> 26:23.325
Yes, Ofjoseph?

26:24.625 --> 26:27.288
Come closer.
It's a secret.

26:33.675 --> 26:34.961
What?

26:44.061 --> 26:45.393
You're not well.

26:48.607 --> 26:49.768
No.

26:51.819 --> 26:53.060
June?

27:09.503 --> 27:11.290
You're out of your mind.

27:14.049 --> 27:16.917
This has to end.
This has to end.

27:20.264 --> 27:22.551
You were supposed to be
one of the strong ones.

27:42.286 --> 27:43.886
There's something wrong.
She cut herself.

28:11.690 --> 28:14.353
Mrs. Waterford said
you cut yourself.

28:16.069 --> 28:17.401
Let me see.

28:18.155 --> 28:19.566
It's all right.

28:26.079 --> 28:27.195
Ouch.

28:28.165 --> 28:29.497
You need stitches.

28:57.778 --> 28:58.894
Come.

28:59.613 --> 29:00.854
Sit.

29:07.996 --> 29:09.532
It's a clean slice.

29:10.415 --> 29:11.781
Just a few more.

29:13.460 --> 29:15.042
You doing okay?

29:17.673 --> 29:19.630
