trying to fix me

29:19.716 --> 29:21.548
if you're just
going to report me.

29:23.178 --> 29:26.012
You're right.
I shouldn't.

29:38.485 --> 29:39.646
Thank you.

29:41.363 --> 29:42.570
I took an oath.

29:43.073 --> 29:44.780
First do no harm.

29:44.866 --> 29:46.107
Am I harming you?

29:48.412 --> 29:49.948
You're torturing her.

29:50.831 --> 29:53.448
She's not my patient,
the child is.

29:53.542 --> 29:54.874
That's bullshit.

29:55.544 --> 29:56.830
Sir.

29:56.920 --> 29:58.081
Hold still.

30:10.225 --> 30:11.966
My mother was a doctor.

30:15.147 --> 30:16.763
She treated pregnant women.

30:17.858 --> 30:19.895
And she always
put her patients,

30:21.028 --> 30:23.111
the women, first.

30:24.531 --> 30:27.319
Things were different
when she practiced medicine.

30:28.910 --> 30:30.026
Did she get out?

30:30.120 --> 30:31.156
No.

30:34.207 --> 30:35.869
I'm sure you miss her.

30:39.171 --> 30:40.628
Where did she practice?

30:40.756 --> 30:43.499
Somerville.
For the most part.

30:47.346 --> 30:49.303
Holly Maddox.

30:53.018 --> 30:54.179
Well,

30:55.103 --> 30:57.937
now I know why you took
a swipe at Mrs. Waterford.

30:58.899 --> 31:00.481
Dr. Maddox.

31:01.610 --> 31:03.272
Dr. Maddox, she was scary.

31:06.365 --> 31:08.948
Yeah. She is.

31:11.787 --> 31:12.994
Was.

31:14.790 --> 31:16.281
I don't actually know.

31:24.549 --> 31:27.087
You should know
I was going to kill Serena.

31:29.846 --> 31:31.132
And her.

31:33.308 --> 31:34.469
And you, too.

31:40.816 --> 31:42.352
I warned them.

31:43.360 --> 31:46.819
I said, "You can't leave
that girl in here,

31:47.489 --> 31:50.448
"praying for months on end."

31:52.536 --> 31:55.074
The brain atrophies
in isolation

31:56.248 --> 31:57.830
and breeds despair.

32:03.463 --> 32:05.830
How long have you had
suicidal thoughts?

32:07.717 --> 32:09.083
Homicidal.

32:09.177 --> 32:12.511
Doing any of the things that you
said would put you on the wall,

32:13.140 --> 32:14.676
and you know it.

32:16.309 --> 32:18.346
So, how long?

32:22.899 --> 32:24.265
I don't know.

32:31.867 --> 32:33.074
Since I realized

32:33.160 --> 32:35.527
I probably won't see
my daughters again.

32:43.170 --> 32:44.752
You feel hopeless?

32:46.006 --> 32:47.497
How should I feel?

32:56.933 --> 33:00.097
Doctor, she's someone's
child, too.

33:07.986 --> 33:10.023
I honor the Handmaid's life

33:12.532 --> 33:14.319
by saving her child.

33:19.915 --> 33:21.827
How will you honor
your daughters?

33:29.382 --> 33:31.089
Try not to get that wet.

33:34.638 --> 33:36.129
Under His eye.

35:25.915 --> 35:28.032
Okay. Take that.

35:29.294 --> 35:31.126
Here we go, gentlemen.

