42:45.271 --> 42:46.762
A space pirate.

43:04.749 --> 43:06.035
It's okay.

43:07.627 --> 43:08.993
It's all right.

43:10.213 --> 43:11.420
I'm here.

43:13.591 --> 43:15.048
I'll be right here.

43:24.977 --> 43:27.435
