have another reason.

43:51.963 --> 43:54.421
They just take everything
from you, you know.

43:56.801 --> 43:58.212
They really do.

44:04.058 --> 44:06.801
Oh, your son,

44:08.396 --> 44:09.978
he's beautiful.

44:11.440 --> 44:13.352
Oh, he's...

