he's just like you.

44:31.377 --> 44:32.663
He's a fighter.

44:39.135 --> 44:43.004
And he doesn't deserve
to grow up in this place.

44:47.018 --> 44:49.010
He deserves to be free.

44:52.064 --> 44:54.272
They all deserve to be free.

44:58.362 --> 45:00.775
So, Natalie...

45:09.415 --> 45:11.122
I'm gonna get them out.

45:13.836 --> 45:16.328
I'm gonna get out
as many children as I can.

45:18.966 --> 45:21.800
I don't really
know how yet, but...

45:25.473 --> 45:27.055
I swear to you,

45:30.978 --> 45:32.594
I'm gonna get them out.

45:39.528 --> 45:42.692
Because Gilead should
know how this feels.

45:46.786 --> 45:48.448
It's their turn to hurt.

45:58.756 --> 46:00.088
All right.

46:01.842 --> 46:03.208
It's okay.

46:03.844 --> 46:05.255
It's all right.

